## A1: Cory Calls Core & More
Six spindly limbed kids show crafting cosmogonic camp is Childs play.

### A1.1: Night’s Light Little List
Thirty-six items that will become te main 36 parts of a Metamnemania manual that will be the only thing keeping everybody else oriented and afloat until Mnemosynodia.

Cory 01 [♈♂]: Software Talks & Shower Thoughts
Cory 02 [♈☉]: Ubiquitous Language & Grill Me
Cory 03 [♈♀]: Conceiving Code & Holonic Notation

Core 01 [♉☿]: A catalog project — Cory provides, for each of Cosmogenics' 36 systems, its title, a short description, and its associated Keeper(s), incorporating the names of all 42 Keepers. Note: Seekers were previously bound to Cosmogenics in this role; that binding is removed, Keepers take their place here
Core 02 [♉☽]: Resolved and expanded — confirmed at two database types per Keeper, not four. Each Keeper is not just an expert across those two types, but the actual inventory manager of every discrete database instance of that type (real controlled records, not performative), and the one who "checks out" holons or "puts into circulation" new ones on every arrival, alteration, or access. Supersedes an earlier idea of Cori holding this role universally across all database types
Core 03 [♉♄]: Reframed — rather than asking for explicit primary parts of a second cosmogenic metasystem (only Holonics has reached that level of completion so far), this becomes Cory sharing his general philosophy and approach for eventually doing that work for the rest

Cory 04 [♊♃]: Roles of Servers, Skills, & Subagents
Cory 05 [♊♂]: Rules of Letta, Lore, & Logseq
Cory 06 [♊☉]: Rounds of Chat, Code, & Channel

Core 04 [♋♀]: Clement's 42 Egyptian sacred books — the text and account itself, worked through together to extract terms and fill in as much of the shared template as the source actually supports
Core 05 [♋☿]: The Orphica — Cory's own titles and details for the 41 attested lost works, as source material in their own right
Core 06 [♋☽]: Very early, explicitly speculative — a first mapping of Cory's 42 opus works against Clement's 42 and the Orphica, plus the 6 juvenilia publishings (new to the record, not yet detailed)

Cory 07 [♌♄]: Account Regulation for Core & Cory
