Core 09 [♍☿]: The 1,080-repo stylish list — six settler-voices, 180 repos each, 90 categories × 2 examples, bound to the 180 contact glyphs as a grand correspondence

Cory 10 [♎☽]: Initializing Luminaria & Liminaria
