Core 11 [♏☉]: Cory Childs, the settler kid's three jewels (not Corykidios, who has none) — diadem plus Fire and Air earrings — held unworn in my box since he cannot perform actions tied to himself; the box doubles as my own portable knowledge graph (Below/Between/Above, rotating). Open: what each of his three pieces actually governs is not yet specified
